Title: CourtSightR
Description: A lightweight terminal-run NBA analytics tool that loads local CSV game data,
    cleans it, computes performance splits, and exports summaries and plots for
    exploratory sports analysis.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: CourtSightR
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Suggests: readr, dplyr, tidyr, ggplot2, optparse
